text: Samuel Yves Oum Gwet (born 14 December 1997) is a Cameroonian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Rheindorf Altach. ==International career== On 9 October 2020, Gouet made his international debut for Cameroon in a friendly match against Japan. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Austrian Football Bundesliga players Category:Cameroonian footballers Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:SC Rheindorf Altach players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Cameroon international footballers Category:Cameroonian expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Austria
